text: Annelie Larsson (born 23 August 1964) is a Swedish rower. She competed at the 1984 Summer Olympics and the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Sweden Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm
